  "body": "### Description\r\nAs a user of Bonsai, I want to have general stability so that my node can keep running with high up-time and no errors, so that my staking rig is stable. \r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n* Bonsai resiliency improvements that resolve the challenges around state-root mismatches and other errors like RLP errors during normal operations. This acceptance can include extending snapshot functionality for more case handling or reviewing/refactoring Bonsai code for post-Merge context. \r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Run Besu in Bonsai mode\r\n2. Wait for stateroot mismatch with concurrency \r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** [What you expect to happen]\r\n- Bonsai runs without issue \r\n\r\n**NEED SCOPE / TIME ESTIMATE** ",
